name: NBI Global Real Assets Income ETF
longDescription: The NBI Global Real Assets Income ETFs investment objective is to provide income and long-term capital growth while focusing on hedging against inflation. It invests, directly or through investments in securities of other mutual funds, in a portfolio comprised primarily of common shares of companies located around the world in industry sectors associated with real assets.
